divs: Sighting DetailsFebruary 2nd 2011. I took photos of odd clouds to me. Four months later I downloaded my phone pics onto my computer. Three months after that I decided to look for UFOs on my photos. I ran into these three back to back photos. I zoomed and enhanced and found, what I believe is two clouds one UFO. You be the judge.
Summary: did not see while taking photos, only looking at clouds
